Discover Precious Metals

ETF Securities is one of the world’s leading innovators of exchange traded products (ETPs). We are independent pioneers, beginning in 2003 as the developer of the world’s first gold ETP, and later the first oil ETP6. In the U.S., we are a specialist commodity ETP provider that offers investors a broad suite of physically-backed precious metal ETFs. Explore gold, silver, platinum and palladium to better understand, "Why invest in precious metals?"




