About Us





Globally
ETF Securities provides accessible investment solutions, enabling investors to intelligently diversify their portfolios beyond traditional asset classes and strategies. We are pioneers in specialist investments, having developed the world’s first gold exchange traded commodity6. Today we offer one of the most comprehensive ranges of specialist exchange traded products (ETPs) covering commodities, FX, fixed income and equities traded on major exchanges across the world. Using that pioneering spirit, our unrivaled expertise and by working with leading third parties, we seek out the most relevant opportunities and make them accessible to investors as intelligent alternatives.





United States
ETF Securities U.S. is a specialist commodity Exchange Traded Product (ETP) provider, backed by a global track record of innovation. Our approach is built on understanding investors’ changing needs to construct accessible solutions, enabling them to diversify their portfolios beyond traditional asset classes and strategies. We produce timely and impactful market insights to support advisors, and their clients, in reaching informed investment decisions.





33 Act Offering
We offer investors a broad suite of physically-backed precious metal ETFs in the U.S., offering the only U.S.-traded physically-backed platinum and palladium in an ETF structure. With our “GLTR” basket, we became the first in the U.S. to offer a physically-backed precious metal basket ETF to hold gold, silver, platinum and palladium.

 


